channel.title: Delta Source Cant Find .cfg Files!
channel.description:
Hi everyone, I just downloaded a delta source and when I run it, it cant find any of the configuration files even though they are there.

PLEASE POST IF YOU KNOW THE REASON WHY!

item.title: Delta Source Cant Find .cfg Files!
item.dc:creator: @Shorty626 Shorty626
item.description:

Since OSX is based on *NIX type systems, the directory structure will be case sensitive. You will need to either rename the directories to the proper case as it is in your serverâ€™s source code, or you need to change the source code to match the case the directories are already in.
